reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful washi tape!!!
reviews.reviewText: This is beautiful tape!!! I saw other reviewers saying there's no gold foil on them, it's not advertised as having gold anything on them. I saw someone else say there's hardly anything on it and they feel they've been ripped off. That's why reading descriptions before you buy is very important. There is 9 feet of tape on each roll. That's how it's supposed to be - that's how it's advertised. Some rolls are wider than the others. I don't feel it's fair for someone to leave a bad review for getting exactly what was advertised. All washi tape is somewhat opaque until you tape it to something. It always looks more colorful when all rolled up. For the price, you can't beat it. It's beautiful, and there are so many designs and colors to choose from.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Are not as vibrant as pictures
reviews.reviewText: Are not as vibrant in color and rolls are thin. When doing a page dashboard you will finish a whole roll in a planner the size of the happy planner. The adhesive is just fine if you're using it on plain planner paper. Satisfied overall.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Impressed with the quality and beauty of these
reviews.reviewText: Great product. The patterns were even prettier in person than the site shows when ordering. The price is fabulous too. Ordering some more tonight to include in gifts for my craft friends.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Very pretty, but adhesive is very weak. Bummer.
reviews.reviewText: I bought these washi tapes to put on 100 tubes of homemade lip balm I made to give as gifts. I wiped the tubes down really well to make sure there was no lip balm residue on the outside that would prevent the tapes from sticking. Even so, they all peeled right off almost immediately. They are VERY pretty and were exactly the look I wanted, but since they didn't stick to the smooth plastic tubes, they wouldn't work for my purpose, so I had to buy something else to use instead (and the other tapes I ended up using stuck to the tubes just fine). Maybe they would work better for paper crafts or some other purpose though? I'll try to find a use for them somewhere...

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute, but more like starter pack.
reviews.reviewText: I really like these and they are super cute. Like many other reviews said, they are not as vibrant as I initially expected. These are also not very large roles, so this seems more like a sampler set. Over all I do like these other than the minor things mentioned.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Doesn't look anything like the pictures. Actual product is dull and disappointing. There is not shiny gold in the tape.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Don't trust the photos
reviews.reviewText: The tape in reality is much duller than what the photos show. The photos also (probably because the tape looks so bright) make it seem like there would be some shimmery parts to the tape. There is no shine at all anywhere. The rolls are still pretty and I will still use them, but I did expect prettier tape.
